{
  "stem": "4113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We found out the following morning that they were all executed and killed in-- in a forest preserve in Brzozow which was a little town not far from our town.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I then found out because there was a German who was an SA man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he wore-- he was a dispatcher of all trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was our neighbor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he had taken liking to me all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was a homosexual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he would accost me, not infrequently, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He would come to our house and tell my mother he needed me because there was going to be an air raid.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I ought to come over to his apartment, you know, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was a dispatcher of the trucks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So the following day, the maid-- his maid, who was a maid that then worked for the Gestapo, you see, told me the story.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was a Jewish hat maker that lived also in our house below him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He lived on top that German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Paes was his name-- P-A-E-S.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And other guy-- the hat maker lived below him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was telling that-- his maid how the hat maker was shot-- how he wrapped himself around in this prayer shawl, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was praying as he ran into the mass grave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he was laughing his head off at that Paes, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she described that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She told me that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, they were killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the meantime, the Gestapo went through the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Fortunately, they didn't catch my mother and my family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They'd catch anybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they shot a number of people whom they called that did not go out to the cattle place.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
